{"id":23670,"type":4,"name":"Titan Quest","name_cn":"泰坦之旅","date":"2006-06-26","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/23/5d/23670_du1jY.jpg","rating":{"rank":2657,"total":64,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":1,"6":15,"7":20,"8":22,"9":3,"10":2},"score":7.2},"summary":"《泰坦之旅》是由Iron Lore Entertainment开发，THQ发行的动作角色扮演游戏。本作设定于上古神话时代，彼时人类文明正在经历浩劫，神祗不再眷顾人类，神话中的妖魔鬼怪遍布山野。玩家扮演一名英雄，行经古希腊、古埃及经过美索不达米亚到达中国，一路斩妖除魔，和源自希腊、埃及和东方神话（……西方人眼中的东方神话）中的妖魔鬼怪进行殊死搏斗，最后回到奥林匹斯山，击败泰坦巨人堤丰，迎接游戏的结局。\r\n游戏方式近似于《暗黑破坏神》，采用全3D引擎，拥有日夜循环效果。值得一提的是游戏没有设定固定的“职业”，而是提供8大技能专精门类，下设不同的技能，玩家最多可以选择其中的其中的两个门类进行修炼，摸索不同的机能组合。橙蓝绿紫的装备系统依旧少不了，只是没有随机地图略微有些失色。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>泰坦之旅</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/17998\">Iron Lore Entertainment</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/16404\">THQ</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>Nintendo Switch</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ARPG</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2006-06-26</li>","collection":{"on_hold":3,"dropped":5,"wish":10,"collect":85,"doing":2},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":19},{"name":"ARPG","count":12},{"name":"RPG","count":11},{"name":"THQ","count":6},{"name":"奇幻","count":3},{"name":"2006","count":2},{"name":"普通游戏","count":1},{"name":"GOG","count":1},{"name":"欧美系","count":1},{"name":"刷刷刷","count":1},{"name":"汉化","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"staff":[{"id":16404,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/b5/f5/16404_prsn_IwyQE.jpg","name":"THQ","desc":"发行"},{"id":17998,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/72/c0/17998_prsn_2Gs44.jpg","name":"Iron Lore Entertainment","desc":"开发"}],"relations":[{"id":449953,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1d/38/449953_d22hx.jpg","title":"Titan Quest II","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/449953"},{"id":129280,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f5/fb/129280_MYLy2.jpg","title":"Titan Quest: Immortal Throne","type":"资料片、外传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/129280"},{"id":253037,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/12/76/253037_E70Oy.jpg","title":"Titan 